        {
          "type": "explanation",
          "name": "PATHFINDING SEARCH RANGES",
          "definition": "The maximum ranges to which firing point evaluations will do pathfinding searches. INCREASING THESE VALUES WILL ALMOST CERTAINLY HAVE A NEGATIVE IMPACT ON PERFORMANCE."
        },
